## Additional Terms for Azure Resources

This software deploys Azure resources which may incur costs. Users are responsible for:
- Understanding Azure pricing and billing
- Monitoring resource usage and costs
- Properly managing and decommissioning resources
- Ensuring compliance with applicable regulations

## Security and Compliance Notice

This software implements security controls and configurations for Azure AI services.
Users are responsible for:
- Validating security configurations meet their requirements
- Implementing additional security measures as needed
- Ensuring compliance with applicable regulations and standards
- Regular security reviews and updates

## Data Protection Notice

Azure AI services may process personal data. Users must:
- Ensure appropriate data protection measures
- Comply with applicable privacy regulations (GDPR, CCPA, etc.)
- Implement proper consent and data handling procedures
- Consider data residency and sovereignty requirements
